            </p>
			<div class="hero-image" style="background-image: url('./../../public/tnd.jpeg');"></div>
        </section>
		<br>
        <section class="mission">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                At TND, we believe learning extends beyond the classroom. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced coder, our collaborative environment supports your growth. From mentorship opportunities to group projects, we are dedicated to fostering a space where developers of all levels can thrive.
